### GraphQL Endpoint
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5002
@graphqlEndpoint = {{baseUrl}}/graphql

### Get All Audit Logs (No Filters)
POST {{graphqlEndpoint}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query { auditLogs { id action entityType entityId userId ipAddress timestamp } }"
}

### Get Audit Logs with Date Range Filter
POST {{graphqlEndpoint}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query GetAuditLogs($fromDate: DateTime, $toDate: DateTime) { auditLogs(fromDate: $fromDate, toDate: $toDate) { id action entityType entityId userId timestamp } }",
  "variables": {
    "fromDate": "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z",
    "toDate": "2026-12-31T23:59:59Z"
  }
}

